...New SYNOPSIS, SHORT TERM, LONG TERM, MARINE...

.SYNOPSIS...
Issued at 350 AM PDT Fri Mar 21 2025

No major changes to the forecast as light rain should stay confined
to northwest CA, perhaps grazing the across northern Sonoma County
late tonight. Otherwise, dry weather persists under partly to mostly
cloudy skies. Temperatures will be near or just below normal today
with highs peaking in the mid 50s to low 60s along the coast and
generally in the 60s for inland areas.

&&

.SHORT TERM...
(Today and tonight)
Issued at 350 AM PDT Fri Mar 21 2025

No major changes to the forecast as light rain should stay confined
to northwest CA, perhaps grazing the across northern Sonoma County
late tonight. Otherwise, dry weather persists under partly to mostly
cloudy skies. Temperatures will be near or just below normal today
with highs peaking in the mid 50s to low 60s along the coast and
